des: Our goal in this project is a service that provides people with any information they want to know about Yarmouk University. Now one of the services available in our project is to provide information about the colleges and departments within any college and some information related to the deans of the colleges and head, vice head of any department. And some courses inside the Queen Rania Center, and the user can inquire about hours in terms of number and hourly wages in the regular and parallel system. With this project, we strive to save time and effort on the user.
